@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tlnbsq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.36)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.77)) * v0)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.41))
    v1 = (wp.abs(0.10) / wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.79)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((tmp + 0.69 / v1 + 0.58) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.51)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
